  <p>This post describes the work done during my time as Electrical Design Head at Team Solaris of Delhi Technological University. We participated in two global competitions and our cars were flagged off and parised by the President of India.</p>
</blockquote>

<p><a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/DTUs-solar-car-goes-to-Australia/articleshow/10025011.cms">Times of India</a> reports : 
